getQNameFromElement

public static javax.xml.namespace.QName getQNameFromElement(org.w3c.dom.Element aDocInstance,
                                                            java.lang.String aElementName)
Gets a QName value from the doc instance at the given Element name. The doc instance must have a child Element with the given name and that child element must be a complex type of the type tns:AeQName (as found in the ActiveBPEL XMLDB schema). If the value is not present or is empty, then null is returned.
